thread.title: BRIEF-Venture Corporation Proposes To Acquire Property Located In Milpitas, California For $29.4 Mln

author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Venture Corporation Proposes To Acquire Property Located In Milpitas, California For $29.4 Mln

organizations.name: brief-venture corporation proposes to acquire property located in milpitas

text:
Jan 18 (Reuters) - Venture Corporation Ltd:
* ‍ANNOUNCES PROPOSED ACQUISITION OF PROPERTY LOCATED IN MILPITAS, CALIFORNIA, UNITED STATES OF AMERICA
* UNIT BUYS FREEHOLD PROPERTY IN UNITED STATES OF AMERICA FOR US$29.4 MLN​
* ‍PROPOSED ACQUISITION IS NOT EXPECTED TO HAVE ANY MATERIAL IMPACT ON NET EPS OF GROUP FOR FINANCIAL YEAR ENDING 31 DEC 2018​ Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage:
